# Next.js SEO Layer Rules

## SEO Mindset

Kurdish content is historically underrepresented on the internet. Every page you optimize for search engines is a step toward making Kurdish culture visible to the world. Think about a young Kurd searching Google for content in Kurmanji or Sorani — your SEO work determines whether they find Nubar or nothing at all. Treat every meta tag, every structured data snippet, every sitemap entry as an act of digital cultural preservation.

The `next-seo/` directory contains the SSG/ISR layer for search engine optimization.

## Page Requirements

Every page under `next-seo/app/` must include:

1. **`generateMetadata()`** — dynamic title, description, Open Graph, Twitter Card
2. **JSON-LD structured data** — Article, Person, or Organization schema
3. **`generateStaticParams()`** — for SSG of popular content

```typescript
export async function generateMetadata({ params }: Props): Promise<Metadata> {
  const post = await getPost(params.id);
  return {
    title: `${post.content.slice(0, 60)} | Nûbar`,
    description: post.content.slice(0, 160),
    openGraph: {
      title: post.content.slice(0, 60),
      description: post.content.slice(0, 160),
      images: post.media_urls?.[0] ? [{ url: post.media_urls[0] }] : [],
      type: 'article',
    },
    twitter: {
      card: 'summary_large_image',
      title: post.content.slice(0, 60),
    },
  };
}
```

## Security

- **NEVER** expose `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY` to client components
- Use server components only for Supabase queries with service role
- Mark client components explicitly with `'use client'`

## Content Strategy

- Include Kurdish keywords in meta descriptions
- Support multiple scripts (Latin for Kurmanji, Arabic for Sorani)
- Use `lang` and `dir` attributes correctly in HTML:
  ```html
  <html lang="ku" dir="ltr">   <!-- Kurmanji -->
  <html lang="ckb" dir="rtl">  <!-- Sorani -->
  ```

## Sitemap & Robots

- `sitemap.ts`: dynamically generate from all public posts, profiles, communities
- `robots.ts`: allow all crawlers, reference sitemap URL
- Set `revalidate` for ISR (e.g. `export const revalidate = 3600` for 1-hour refresh)

## Image Optimization

- Use `next/image` for all images with proper `alt` text
- Serve images from CDN (`cdn.nubar.app`)
- Include width/height to prevent layout shift
